*net-snmp-5.0.2a-r1 (4 Aug 2002)

  28 Sep 2002; Owen Stampflee <owen@gentoo.org> :
  Added PPC to KEYWORDS.

  4 Aug 2002; Kyle Manna <nitro@gentoo.org> net-snmp-5.0.2a-r1.ebuild:
  
